: #ffffff;\">Household Mode</h2>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div layer-name=\"Tile — Playful by design\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 482.6666666666667px; top: 655px; width: 474.6666666666667px; height: 461px; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; background-color: #07060a; border: 1px solid transparent;\">\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; inset: 0; overflow: hidden; \"><video src=\"paper-asset:///Users/jessechapo/Dropbox/Websites/chapolito.com/chapolito-2026/images/messenger-kids/missed-call.mp4\" style=\"display: block; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;\" loop playsinline></video></div>\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(15deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.72) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.34) 28%, transparent 50%); opacity: 0.72;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; left: 20px; right: 20px; bottom: 18px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-weight: 700; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.03em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);\">Messenger Kids</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.02; letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: #ffffff;\">Playful by design</h2>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div layer-name=\"Tile — Family Messaging\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 961.3333333333334px; top: 655px; width: 474.6666666666667px; height: 461px; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; background-color: #07060a; border: 1px solid transparent;\">\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; inset: 0; overflow: hidden; background: radial-gradient(120% 100% at 50% 0%, #2c2336, #14101c);\"><video src=\"paper-asset:///Users/jessechapo/Dropbox/Websites/chapolito.com/chapolito-2026/images/life360/closing-the-loop.mp4\" style=\"display: block; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain;\" loop playsinline></video></div>\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(15deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.72) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.34) 28%, transparent 50%); opacity: 0.72;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; left: 20px; right: 20px; bottom: 18px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-weight: 700; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.03em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);\">Life360</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.02; letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: #ffffff;\">Family Messaging</h2>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>"
